Snai Names Former Lottomatica CFO Stefano Bortoli as New CEO

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-06-01T21:10:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-01/snai-names-former-lottomatica-cfo-stefano-bortoli-as-new-ceo.html
Snai SpA (SNA)  appointed Stefano Bortoli,
formerly chief financial officer of  Lottomatica SpA (LTO) , as chief
executive officer, the company said in an e-mailed statement
today. The board also co-opted Bortoli as a board member to
replace Rohan Maxwell, who has resigned, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 